返，一路到油麻地load下停下<br />\n油麻地轉車之後就好順，直到九龍塘又load唔到<br />\n一直到彩虹落車又係load下停下，上返彩虹大堂就好順<br />\n<br />\n搭車入大欖隧道，全死，出隧道就正常返<br />\n反而由羅湖到九龍塘冇乜點斷，可能大部份時間係地面<br />\n<br />\n夜晚係屋企開住twitch成晚冇斷過<br />\n係公司做hotspot update 6gb野都冇斷，仲好快<br />\n<br />\n好唔好用就睇你係邊度用多<br />\n過5gb影響不大，收唔到嘅就點都收唔到"},{"pid":"438dbb898e6baf377a9a60daa5f294eb37e24db0","tid":770431,"uid":59919,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T05:47:34.000Z","msg":"有無得帶號碼過自由鳥？"},{"pid":"31b55079dac4e39e68fb6de474fa1e80250ccb9b","tid":770431,"uid":232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"438dbb898e6baf377a9a60daa5f294eb37e24db0","tid":770431,"uid":59919,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T05:47:34.000Z","msg":"有無得帶號碼過自由鳥？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T06:24:42.000Z","msg":"有，自己上網搵，但要upload身份證"},{"pid":"e1aea6ab8a0cc7f66c90317af29d026a3b1570b8","tid":770431,"uid":232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"31b55079dac4e39e68fb6de474fa1e80250ccb9b","tid":770431,"uid":232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"438dbb898e6baf377a9a60daa5f294eb37e24db0","tid":770431,"uid":59919,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T05:47:34.000Z","msg":"有無得帶號碼過自由鳥？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T06:24:42.000Z","msg":"有，自己上網搵，但要upload身份證"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T06:25:05.000Z","msg":"自己上網搞"},{"pid":"0a0d53057f1fd41012d2f377078a0c4b8a83b326","tid":770431,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77ff0dff84f06c78968b1cbe5b48e2508d05dde8","tid":770431,"uid":37358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:47:30.000Z","msg":"嚟緊諗住轉台，見到sun mobile 118個plan好似幾正，但真心怕佢5gb 之後上唔撚到網，雖然佢claim 5gb之後速度可以高達21mb<br />\n<br />\n之後上網見到自由鳥$140 12gb plan，雖然貴d，但至少個12gb 可以用21mb 全速咁上<br />\n<br />\n唔知巴打點睇呢2個台呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\